msgstr "Verificando Arquivos e Bibliotecas Desatualizados"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/cutting-edge/_index.adoc:886
msgid ""
"Some obsolete files or directories can remain after an update.  These files "
